window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Over 500,000 copies sold.</p> <p>Scott Brick brings to life a heart-stopping, critically acclaimed and bestselling international thriller.</p> <p>Even after they retire, crisis negotiators are haunted by the principal rule of dealing with violent terrorists: Just because the hostages have been released, it doesn't mean it's over.</p> <p>Warning! Highly addictive escapism disguised as fiction. Only commit to this experience if you can tolerate pure adrenaline.</p>"; 
